    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-12-08T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-12-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="363"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d363">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.001J56/a.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Wilson</persName> to President
                            <persName type="to">Juan Isidro Jiménez</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The White House</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-12-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 8, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I most heartily congratulate you upon your inauguration into office and extend to
                    you my most sincere wishes for the peace and prosperity of the Dominican
                    Republic.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Woodrow Wilson</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
